Don’t miss this opportunity to lease one of the only zoned and serviced 1HA sites in Pinkenba .

- 10,130sqm* land parcel
- General Industry B Zone
- Awning 
- Serviced with 3 phase power, water & sewer
- Sealed with bitumen, road base & concrete
- Security fencing, lighting & electric gate
- Currently being used as a transport & logistics facility

Bancroft Road Pinkenba is adjacent to the Brisbane Airport and is populated with modern industrial buildings. 63 Bancroft Road is the last underdeveloped land parcels in the immediate surrounding precinct. Pinkenba forms part of the highly desirable Tradecoast Precinct with access to all major road networks & the Brisbane Airport. Given the location & surrounding transport amenity this location is highly sought after a multitude of corporate industrial occupiers.
